title: Opie Radio-YKWD (SPECIAL) JUL 25 2016 Mon
description:
At first I wasn't going to post this show, because unlike last thursday special which was O&J but with guest hosts, this was a special live edition fill in show of Robert kelly's: You Know What Dude. It's a show I don't listen to but some of you might, so here it is. 



You Know What Dude (SPECIAL) JUL 25 2016 Mon  (03:09:52)

On Today's Show:

DJ DENNIS FALCONE , VIC HENLEY, LUIS J. GOMEZ, TIM DILLON, COLIN HAY.

* Thin Lizzy:"The Rocker".
* DJ Denny kicks things off.
* VIC HENLEY, LUIS J. GOMEZ & TIM DILLON in studio.
* Luis surprised he's on Opie's channel.
* Kerry Ann DePetro will be doing the face painting.
* Discussing Philly.
* Child/Teen years stories.
* Grandparents.
* The Face painting begins.
* The election.
* The Village People.
* Roland's face paint & Coon hunting.
* Bobby HATED Batman V Superman.
* A tiger attacks a woman.
* Talking about body weight.
* Discussing what face paint designs to get.
* Remembering high school dances.
* Bob when he was young & thin pics. 
* Tim's father was in a cover-band.
* Bob's relationship with his father & sister.
* Delaney BBQ is delivered.
* Food talk.
* COLIN HAY stops by.
* A little accents talk.
* Men at work, & music videos.
* Colin talks a bit about his wife.
* Colin performs "Next Year People".
* The plugs.
* Colin performs "Down Under".
* Thanks & face paint winner.
* Marcia Griffiths:"Electric Boogie" (The Electric Slide)
